# Scoped for repo-root-context builds (tester-unified, wheel-builder — both built via
# `docker build -f <dir>/Dockerfile ... /workspaces/vbpub`). Whitelist ONLY what they
# COPY (or, for wheel-builder, may COPY in future — today it's stateless), so the
# build context stays tiny — everything else (.git, .worktrees, logs, other stacks) is
# excluded. NOTE: this whitelist means a repo-root `docker build` sees only these
# dirs; other stacks build from their own subdirectory contexts, not here.
*
!ciu
!cmru
!topos
!nyxloom
!wheel-builder

# Drop heavy/generated content within the whitelisted projects.
**/.git
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.hypothesis
**/.mypy_cache
**/node_modules
**/.worktrees
